--------------------------------------------------------------------
pango-1.6.0-sinhala1.patch
http://bugzilla.gnome.org/show_bug.cgi?id=153517

The original patch to add Sinhala support was created by Harsha Senanayake
for ICU (http://marc.theaimsgroup.com/?t=106354110900001&r=1&w=2)
and later ported to Pango. The Pango patch was ported to the latest
version of Pango, cleaned up and submitted to bugzilla by Anuradha Ratnaweera.
This is the patch that was submitted to bugzilla.

